<p>'I know it is the biggest gift to even be able to carry a child and whatever my body endures I know it is ALWAYS worth it for what is waiting for me at the finish line,' she said.</p>

<p>Hundreds of women praised the 2001 Big Brother contestant for being so open about the 'hectic' side effects, many of which they had experienced themselves. </p>
